column5: Lew hasn't logged on since July 23rd....so I'm assuming he's on vacation....catching muskie after muskie in every lake he visits!!!
I'll ask him this weekend for you.

LOL Cory, looking forward to seeing the both of you (and a few others) this weekend  Lew is fine and catching fish but most importantly he is taken care of his wife and daughter while they recuperate from their surgeries at his lake place, both his gals are doing fine
He has been doing just fine up at his place. Hopefully I can poach his spot on Muskrat before he gets there. HAHAHAHAHA.
Pete don't want to see you two chucking 7/0 trebles at each other, that could get dangerous  See ya on Friday
